text: Matt Moore may refer to: * Matt Moore (actor) (1888–1960), Irish-born American film actor * Matt Moore (American football) (born 1984), American football quarterback * Matt Moore (basketball), National Basketball League player * Matt Moore (musician), guitarist, vocalist, and video director from Southern Missouri * Matt Moore (baseball) (born 1989), Major League Baseball player * Matt Moore (politician) (born 1982), American politician ==See also== * Matthew Moore, American songwriter who collaborated with Joe Cocker and Leon Russell
